rows.label: qev092304_MSG0001
rows.name: Man, life is a real bitch sometimes...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092304_MSG0002
rows.name: Go on. Do it. I got nowhere left to go anyway.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092304_JNK0010
rows.name: Interrogate

rows.label: qev092304_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Ornella why she did this.

rows.label: qev092304_JNK0020
rows.name: Execute

rows.label: qev092304_SEL0021
rows.name: Grant Ornella's wish and take her life.

rows.label: qev092304_MSG0003
rows.name: What? You wanna know why I did it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092304_MSG0004
rows.name: No. Wait.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092304_MSG0005
rows.name:
Why did you do this, Ornella?
Help me understand.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092304_MSG0006
rows.name:
You think anyone would play sidekick
to a naive fool like you for free?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092304_MSG0007
rows.name:
You were popular even before the crash,
and I thought I'd get in on it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092304_MSG0008
rows.name:
Make a quick buck and walk away whistling.
But you kept helping people for FREE![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092304_MSG0009
rows.name:
We were in the red from day one.
All that potential, wasted![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092304_MSG0010
rows.name:
So I sold you out. Then I sold the mims
of your clients to those freaks.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092304_MSG0011
rows.name: That's horrible![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092304_MSG0012
rows.name: Yes, and I belong in hell for what I've done![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092304_MSG0013
rows.name: Now hurry up and send me there.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092304_MSG0014
rows.name: No. Come back to New LA with us.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092304_MSG0015
rows.name: If we explain this... We'll find a way.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092304_MSG0016
rows.name:
I'll vouch for you. Do whatever
it takes to make it right.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092304_MSG0017
rows.name: You make me sick.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092304_MSG0018
rows.name:
Unconditional love? Martyrdom?
What are you trying to gain with that dreck?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092304_MSG0019
rows.name: I'm...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092304_MSG0020
rows.name: I'm not...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092304_MSG0021
rows.name: This is what my father taught me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092304_MSG0022
rows.name:
Yeah, and where'd it get him?
Fleeced and murdered![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092304_MSG0023
rows.name: ......[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092304_MSG0024
rows.name: ......[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092304_MSG0025
rows.name: Aaaah ha ha ha ha![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092304_MSG0026
rows.name:
I'm no different from the ones who
killed your father, Hope.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092304_MSG0027
rows.name: ...Actually, I'm worse.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092304_MSG0028
rows.name: Ornella, no![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092304_MSG0029
rows.name: Nothing you can say will change my mind.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092304_MSG0030
rows.name: Now shut up and die with a little dignity![ST:wait ]
